cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and summarization. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as summarization is a common task in this field. The use of optimization techniques suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-categories. Finally, the use of integer linear optimization suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category.
